{"tid":647684,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［深圳唔好玩？］棄深圳大小梅沙 內地露營軍團五.一攻陷西貢西灣","createTime":"2018-04-30T05:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T17:29:54.000Z","uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9e10d312b5af2bf7693dc882af9dc43b332d37be","tid":647684,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:04:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n內地五一勞動節長假期，大批內地旅客大舉南下來港，一浪接一浪，一團接一團。除了到市區購物外，近年不少內地旅客都喜歡前往郊外，感受大自然。其中西貢水清沙幼的大浪西至咸田灣幾乎完全淪為內地人的後花園。沿岸幾個沙灘遍布顏色歸一，大小一至，秩序井然的陣營。<br />\n<br />\n根據康文署網頁顯示，鹹田灣營地數目共有10個，適合有經驗之遠足及露營人士。記者早上徒步直擊，沿途遇上旗幟分明的內地露營團，部分清晨已拔營離開。不過沙灘上仍留下一個接一個排列有秩露營的印記。不少旅客都帶同露營用品，更自備食水食糧，更有旅行團帶同數十名團友，前往鹹田灣紮營。<br />\n<br />\n有來自廣州及東莞的團友表示，是参加兩日一夜300元的遠足露營團。她們表示，五一黄金周內地景點人潮無處不在。過去沙幼水清的大小梅沙，不過太商業化，環境衛生也沒香港好。家住深圳的黄先生說，愛上香港的郊野公園自然美景，要是用來興建房屋實在太可借。有團友還温馨提示，最好早上五、六點上公厠或洗臉，不然要排大隊輪候。<br />\n<br />\n有住在大嶼山的外籍夫婦，為享受寧靜美景，特別遠足到西貢大浪等海灘。他們說，沒想到在西灣露營，旅客太多吵翻天，令他們難以入睡。在西灣開設士多的村長黎恩說，五一黄金假期未到，內地露營團已殺到，單是西灣已有逾200個營幕。他士多旁的私人土地也已包團方式，出租給內地團紥營。他說現在除了假期、周末或周日，平日也有不少內地客來西貢西灣優美海灘度假。整體有逾70%是內地客。過去賣豆花幾十碗，現在假日便賣200至300碗。還有各類凍飲、即食麵幾乎沽清。<br />\n<br />\n記者現場所見，沙灘未見髒亂，原來背後是清潔承辦商的功勞。有清潔工人說，大早便清理好阻塞洗臉盆的廚餘及雜物。一個假期便要處理700至800袋垃圾，安排船隻運走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525060339_44b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525060339_44b5.jpg&h=121f5be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525060342_1ca3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525060342_1ca3.jpg&h=45664ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525060346_41cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525060346_41cd.jpg&h=387c084e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525060350_feb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525060350_feb5.jpg&h=1b4c9329&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180430/large/1525060354_d532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180430%2Flarge%2F1525060354_d532.jpg&h=55619a1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180430/58135321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58135321&d=o%2B%2Ft6ZNhMNaLeTnMtccsFQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1bac41bc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Ftop%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58135321&h=49f54e6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/top/realtime/article/20180430/58135321</a>"},{"pid":"bc3390be4cde69b3739e0696701db2c46f283f7d","tid":647684,"uid":8048,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲大遷徙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22263cb970488691ceb3c37efe6c466391648b32","tid":647684,"uid":36901,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"一團團咁瘋狂紮晒營仲唔叫商業化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個行為本身已經破壞安寧<br />\n香港人犧牲居住面積保留郊野公園<br />\n都係想留返僅有淨土<br />\n唔係為左益你班陷家產生態破壞團賺錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc31cfcaf773064b903920e3d9c68efd47cee78","tid":647684,"uid":176318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好唔開心"},{"pid":"796931fb6564c74d72f1c69a11103e7a7d480088","tid":647684,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"呢個位6-7年前去<br />\n無人到裸跑裸泳都得<br />\n而家可以爆到咁<br />\n仲要極多艇仔接出入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"601942acaa824047a5a64e6fe9b9b34ab851d180","tid":647684,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T05:25:48.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲入侵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3e3627df4041dd7a92296d3058daefa43b71c6","tid":647684,"uid":169074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T17:29:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}